WHO   — Thom Merrilin — the gleeman with a sword in his heart
WHAT  — A traveling gleeman of patch-cloak, juggling, and tales who is secretly far more.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: the companions — the worldly folk who walk beside the Pattern's chosen  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — He shapes the journey of the Two Rivers folk as their mentor and protector, steadying ordinary lives caught in the Wheel's turning.
HOW   — He moves through the world by craft and grief — a player of royal intrigues, skilled with a knife, masking his depths beneath a bard's performance.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
